Package adrenaline.server.network

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Client
    The clientAPI interface for some client set operation
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientRMIWrapper
    The client socket wrapper class implements Client interface,it will send package from server to client via RMI
    ClientSocketWrapper
    The client socket wrapper class implements Client interface,it will send package from server to client via socket
    LobbyExportable
    The LobbyExportable extends UnicastRemoteObject implements LobbyAPI, to received action request from client terminal and return the result of operation
    ServerCommands
    The ServerCommands class to do some internet operations extends UnicastRemoteObject implements ServerAPI
